summary: Turns that perfectly good house a little bit from Whiterun into a player home, no murder required!
descriptionHtml: This will turn [url=http://elderscrolls.wikia.com/wiki/Drelas%27_Cottage]Drelas' Cottage[/url] into a player home, it's located a little bit from Whiterun and is a nice little place for the player to stay in, I do plan on making it bigger, adding more stuff, eventually making it a hold of it's own, which may not be lore friendly but hey! who doesn't want to own there own city, which may or may not end up bigger than whiterun?
author: ozlore125 aka Enigma
